          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1678378489729-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the veg has softened, drain, then add your <strong>king prawns</strong> to the pan with the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and<strong> ginger</strong> <strong>paste</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until the prawns are cooked through</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1678378493043-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
